  - OneXPlayer AMD
  - OneXPlayer mini AMD
  - OneXPlayer mini AMD PRO
+ - OneXPlayer OneXFly
+ - OneXPlayer X1 A
+ - OneXPlayer X1 i
+ - OneXPlayer X1 mini
+ - OrangePi NEO-01
 
 "Turbo/Silent" button behaviour toggle is only supported on:
  - AOK ZOE A1
  - AOK ZOE A1 PRO
+ - OneXPlayer 2
+ - OneXPlayer 2 Pro
  - OneXPlayer mini AMD (only with updated alpha BIOS)
  - OneXPlayer mini AMD PRO
+ - OneXPlayer OneXFly
+ - OneXPlayer X1 A
+ - OneXPlayer X1 i
+ - OneXPlayer X1 mini
 
